<entry align="left" valign="top"><para>Page pr&eacute;c&eacute;dente</para></entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry align="left" valign="top"><para>m s</para></entry>
<entry align="left" valign="top"><para>&lt;Touche>v:</para></entry>
